<div class="policy-page full-width">

  <div class="policy-page__hero">
    <div class="policy-page__hero-inner">
      <p class="policy-page__eyebrow">Artisans Touch</p>
      <h1 class="policy-page__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="policy-page__rule">
        <span class="policy-page__rule-line"></span>
        <span class="policy-page__rule-diamond"></span>
        <span class="policy-page__rule-line"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-page__body">
    <div class="policy-page__content">

      <p class="policy-intro">At Artisans Touch, your privacy matters to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or make a purchase. By using our site, you consent to the practices described below.</p>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you visit our store or place an order, we may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Personal Identification:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, billing and shipping address.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit/debit card details (processed securely by our payment provider — we do not store card numbers).</li>
          <li><strong>Device &amp; Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, time spent on site, and referral URLs.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small files placed on your device to improve your browsing experience and remember preferences.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Process and fulfil your orders and send order confirmations.</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your purchase, returns, or enquiries.</li>
          <li>Send promotional emails and newsletters (only with your consent).</li>
          <li>Improve our website, products, and customer experience.</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your data with trusted service providers who assist in operating our website and delivering your orders, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Payment processors (e.g. Shopify Payments, Stripe)</li>
          <li>Shipping and logistics partners</li>
          <li>Email marketing platforms (only if you have opted in)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These third parties are required to keep your information confidential and use it only for the purpose of providing their services to us.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance your shopping experience. Cookies help us remember your cart contents, track site usage, and personalise content. You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but this may affect some website features. By continuing to use our site, you consent to our use of cookies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Our website uses SSL encryption for all data transmitted between your browser and our servers. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you.</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal obligations).</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time by clicking &ldquo;Unsubscribe&rdquo; in any email we send.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:artisanstouch@gmail.com">artisanstouch@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites (such as our social media profiles). We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>8. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such data, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. The updated version will be posted on this page with the effective date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section policy-section--contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:artisanstouch@gmail.com">artisanstouch@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +94 11 234 5678</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> No.02, Main Road, Malabe</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .policy-page { grid-column: 1 / -1; width: 100%; }

  .policy-page__hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0f06 0%, #2d1a08 50%, #1a0f06 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px 72px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .policy-page__hero-inner { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .policy-page__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--brand-gold, #c9a96e); margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .policy-page__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 52px; font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff; margin: 0 0 24px; line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .policy-page__rule {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px;
  }
  .policy-page__rule-line {
    width: 80px; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--brand-gold, #c9a96e));
  }
  .policy-page__rule-line:last-child {
    background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--brand-gold, #c9a96e));
  }
  .policy-page__rule-diamond {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--brand-gold, #c9a96e);
    transform: rotate(45deg); flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .policy-page__body {
    background: #fff8f8; padding: 72px 24px 96px;
  }
  .policy-page__content {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .policy-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 17px; color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 48px;
    padding-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8d8cc;
  }

  .policy-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .policy-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-gold, #c9a96e);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .policy-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: #555;
    line-height: 1.85; margin: 12px 0 0;
  }
  .policy-section a {
    color: var(--coral-pink, #ff9696); text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .policy-section ul {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: #555;
    line-height: 1.85; margin: 12px 0 0; padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .policy-section ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

  .policy-section--contact {
    background: #f5e6da; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 36px; margin-top: 56px;
  }
  .policy-section--contact h2 { border-color: var(--coral-pink, #ff9696); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-page__title { font-size: 36px; }
    .policy-page__hero { padding: 56px 20px 52px; }
    .policy-page__body { padding: 48px 20px 72px; }
    .policy-section--contact { padding: 24px 20px; }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Privacy Policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
